pr_title: [Agent] Add JDK13, JDK14 to build matrix

timeline.bodyText: We don't test 6.x for JDK 13/14. We should not indicate those.
timeline.author: wu-sheng
timeline.diffHunk:
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
 # Setup java agent
-1. Agent is available for JDK 8 - 12 in 7.x releases. JDK 1.6 - JDK 12 are supported in all 6.x releases [NOTICE¹](#notice)
+1. Agent is available for JDK 8 - 14 in 7.x releases. JDK 1.6 - JDK 14 are supported in all 6.x releases [NOTICE¹](#notice)
